p:
“na cēdaṁ snānamadr̥ṣṭārtham” ityādibhāṣyaṁ smr̥tyarthavyākhyānaparam;
tasyārthamāha—yastvēvamiti । yastu virōdhaparihārāya āplavanaṁ smr̥tyarthaṁ brūyāt
anyaṁ vā kathañcidadr̥ṣṭārthasaṁskāram, tasyōttaram—“na cēdam” iti bhāṣyēṇa ।।

LG.p:
“taccētpratyayitāt” ityasya yat pratyudāharaṇam “athāpratyayitāt” iti
tat “indriyaviṣayaṁ vā” ityasyāpratyayitavākyaprāmāṇyōdāharaṇasya bādhakam;
“indriyaviṣayaṁ vā” ityasya ca yat pratyudāharaṇam “anindriyaviṣayaṁ vā” iti
tadapi “taccētpratyayitāt” ityasya śrōturanindriyaviṣayōdāharaṇasya bādhakam;

dōṣavarjitaiḥ kāraṇairjanyamānatvadityasya ca ghaṭādāvapi bhāvādanaikāntikatvam;
buddhitvaviśēṣaṇapakṣē ca smr̥tijñānēnānaikāntikatvam । naitadēvam; ayathārthabhāvā-
bhāvō'tra pratijñātārthaḥ; na ca kaścid dōṣaḥ ।।

“kathaṁ punarasāvanarthaḥ?” ityasya uttarabhāṣyam “hiṁsā hi sā, sā ca
pratiṣiddhā” iti । ētadvikalpya dūṣayitumāha—cōdanālakṣaṇamityardhēna । yadi
tāvatkaraṇabhūtāḥ śyēnādayō'tra hiṁsāśabdēnābhidhīyantē, tadōpakramōpasaṁhārayōrvirōdhaḥ;
